cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is about image retrieval using hashing techniques and deep neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of multi-view methods and deep learning, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper proposes a new hashing method, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
